He's a new kid in my home room,
just moved in from across town.

06:02.195 --> 06:03.754
He's a funny guy.
You're gonna love him.

06:03.864 --> 06:04.990
- Yeah?
- Yeah. Hey.

06:05.098 --> 06:07.567
How are you?
How are you? How are you?

06:07.667 --> 06:09.328
Yeah.

06:09.436 --> 06:10.801
Arthur Godfrey, right?

06:10.904 --> 06:13.635
Yeah, the old redhead.
Pretty good, huh?

06:13.740 --> 06:16.835
Oh, uh, Richie Cunningham,
this here is Malph Ralph.

06:16.943 --> 06:18.570
You got it backwards.

06:18.678 --> 06:20.942
It's Ralph... Malph, see?

06:21.047 --> 06:22.640
I got it. So does my T-shirt.

06:22.749 --> 06:24.046
-(Ralph laughs)
- Oh.

06:24.150 --> 06:26.176
Well, either way, it's, uh,
very nice meeting you.

06:26.286 --> 06:27.754
Yeah, everyone says that.
(laughs)

06:27.854 --> 06:29.322
Say, did you two guys
hear the one

06:29.422 --> 06:31.152
