07:07.060 --> 07:08.459
Hi.

07:10.163 --> 07:12.188
Something I could do for you?

07:16.102 --> 07:18.332
Oh, well, I... I guess not.

07:25.445 --> 07:27.743
Been nice talking to you.

07:30.183 --> 07:32.151
