07:32.252 --> 07:34.243
Yeah, you rang, Fonzie?

07:35.789 --> 07:39.156
Oh, yeah, Fonz, there's three
nerds sitting in your booth.

07:39.259 --> 07:41.751
What do you want me
to do to 'em, huh?

07:41.861 --> 07:43.625
Some, uh,
free dental work maybe?

07:43.730 --> 07:46.165
