in three years.

07:49.536 --> 07:51.698
Wait a minute, wait a minute...
now, you guys...

07:51.805 --> 07:54.831
You guys wouldn't hit a man
in glasses now, would you?

07:57.210 --> 07:59.907
You and your pals
are in big trouble.

08:00.013 --> 08:01.503
Pals? What pals?

08:01.614 --> 08:03.310
I don't know these guys.
I'm new here.

08:03.416 --> 08:04.850
As a matter of fact,
I just met 'em.

08:04.951 --> 08:06.112
See you at school, strangers.

08:06.219 --> 08:07.812
