08:42.155 --> 08:44.123
With that nail.

08:46.860 --> 08:49.693
Yeah, you got it real deep, too.

08:49.796 --> 08:51.594
-(Richie clears his throat)
- Yeah, real deep. Oh.

08:51.698 --> 08:54.258
Look, uh, let me, explain this
to you, kid.

08:54.367 --> 08:56.392
You see, we gotta
defend our turf,

08:56.503 --> 08:57.800
