is just full of malarkey.

09:06.780 --> 09:09.874
Okay, enough gabbing.
Let's fight.

09:09.983 --> 09:11.041
- Fight?!
- RICHIE: No, no!

09:11.151 --> 09:13.244
No way I'm gonna
fight over a booth.

09:13.353 --> 09:15.344
Well, you're gonna have to,
dope.

09:15.455 --> 09:18.220
'Cause you're gonna get creamed,
anyways.

